---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import CTASection from "../components/CTASection.astro";
import FAQ from "../components/FAQ.astro";
import PlatformShowcase from "../components/PlatformShowcase.astro";

const title = "Email Marketing Platform & Systems for Developers | Laravel Mail";
const description = "Discover the ultimate email marketing platform for technical teams. Master email growth, automation, and deliverability with Laravel Mail's self-hosted software.";
const keywords = "email marketing, email marketing platform, email marketing software, automated email marketing, email marketing for small business, email marketing systems, email marketing campaign";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} keywords={keywords}>
    <section class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pt-28 md:pb-24 overflow-hidden relative">
        <div class="container-custom relative">
            <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
                <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand-primary/10 border border-brand-primary/20 text-brand-primary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
                    Pillar Page
                </div>
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-black leading-tight text-white mb-8">
                    Email Marketing Platform <br/><span class="gradient-text">for Developers</span>
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-10">
                    Step into the future of <strong>email marketing</strong>. Whether you're an indie hacker or an enterprise team, 
                    our <strong>email marketing platform</strong> is designed to scale your <strong>email marketing systems</strong> 
                    and deliver high-performing <strong>automated email marketing</strong> campaigns.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
                    <a href="/buy" class="btn btn-primary px-8 py-4 text-lg">Get Started with Laravel Mail</a>
                    <a href="#overview" class="text-white hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors font-medium">Explore the Systems ↓</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="overview" class="py-20 bg-brand-bg/50">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What is the Modern Email Marketing Platform?</h2>
                    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300">
                        <p>
                            A modern <strong>email marketing platform</strong> is more than just a sender; it's a core component of your 
                            product's communication layer. In today's landscape, <strong>email marketing software</strong> must be 
                            high-performance, developer-friendly, and privacy-first.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            For growing businesses, <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> often means juggling expensive 
                            SaaS costs. Laravel Mail redefines this by providing professional <strong>email marketing systems</strong> 
                            that you own. This allows you to scale your <strong>email marketing campaign</strong> efforts without 
                            paying a "subscriber tax."
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We view <strong>email marketing</strong> as a technical challenge that deserves a technical solution. 
                            By self-hosting your <strong>email marketing software</strong>, you gain absolute control over your 
                            deliverability, data, and user experience.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-brand-primary/5 border border-brand-primary/20 rounded-2xl p-8">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Core Email Marketing Pillars</h3>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-300">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">01.</span>
                            <span><strong>Email Systems:</strong> Robust infrastructure for high-volume delivery and list management.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">02.</span>
                            <span><strong>Automated Email Marketing:</strong> Building smart, event-driven communication flows.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">03.</span>
                            <span><strong>Deliverability:</strong> Ensuring your <strong>email marketing campaign</strong> hits the inbox.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                            <span class="text-brand-primary font-bold">04.</span>
                            <span><strong>Segmentation:</strong> Targeting the right users with the right <strong>email marketing systems</strong>.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container-custom text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Automation & Software Excellence</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                The best <strong>email marketing service</strong> is one that integrates seamlessly with your existing stack. 
                Automation is no longer a luxury—it's the engine of modern growth.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">API First</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Connect your <strong>email marketing software</strong> to any application using our robust developer API.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Zero Contact Tax</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Scale your <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> to millions of contacts without increasing costs.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 hover:border-brand-primary/50 transition-all duration-300">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Total Ownership</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400">
                        Your <strong>email marketing systems</strong>, your data, your rules. No shared IPs or SaaS gatekeepers.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 bg-brand-primary/5 relative">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                 <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">10M+</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Monthly Emails</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">99%</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Inbound Reputation</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">∞</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Subscriber Growth</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-brand-bg border border-white/10 rounded-xl text-center">
                            <span class="block text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-2">100%</span>
                            <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Data Sovereignty</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Systems Built for Laravel Developers</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 font-medium">
                        Laravel is the perfect ecosystem for building world-class <strong>email marketing systems</strong>. 
                        Our <strong>email marketing software</strong> leverages the power of Eloquent, Queues, and Notifications 
                        to deliver a premium <strong>automated email marketing</strong> experience.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-400">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Full control over your <strong>email marketing campaign</strong> triggers and timing.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Supports advanced <strong>email marketing systems</strong> like multi-stage drips and custom logic.
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
                             <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                             Detailed reporting and analytics for every <strong>email marketing service</strong> interaction.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <PlatformShowcase />

    <FAQ />

    <section class="py-20">
        <div class="container-custom">
            <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-400 text-sm">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-4">Deep Dive: Master Your Email Marketing Software</h2>
                <p>
                     To truly excel in <strong>email marketing</strong>, one must understand the underlying <strong>email systems</strong>. 
                     Scaling your <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> requires a shift from manual sending to 
                     sophisticated <strong>automated email marketing</strong>. This transition is made possible by high-quality 
                     <strong>email marketing software</strong> that puts the developer in charge.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Every <strong>email marketing campaign</strong> you send is an opportunity to learn about your audience. 
                    By using advanced <strong>email marketing systems</strong>, you can perform deep-dive analytics on your 
                    <strong>email marketing service</strong> performance. From subject line optimization to send-time analysis, 
                    the right <strong>email marketing platform</strong> makes data actionable.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The future of <strong>email marketing</strong> is owned. As third-party data becomes more restricted, 
                    owning your <strong>email marketing systems</strong> becomes a massive competitive advantage. 
                    By building your <strong>marketing automation</strong> on Laravel Mail, you ensure that your 
                    <strong>email marketing software</strong> is future-proof and fully compliant with evolving standards.
                </p>
                
                <p>
                    A professional <strong>email marketing platform</strong> is the lifeblood of any modern SaaS or e-commerce business. 
                    Without reliable <strong>email marketing software</strong>, user retention and growth become significantly more difficult. 
                    Our mission is to provide the best <strong>email marketing for small business</strong> and enterprise developers alike, 
                    ensuring that <strong>automated email marketing</strong> is accessible and powerful for everyone.
                </p>
                <p>
                    When choosing an <strong>email marketing service</strong>, consider the long-term implications of data ownership. 
                    Shared <strong>email marketing systems</strong> can put your reputation at risk. 
                    With a dedicated <strong>email marketing platform</strong>, you are the master of your <strong>email marketing campaign</strong> 
                    destiny. Join the thousands of developers who have switched to a better way of doing <strong>email marketing</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection />
</Layout>
